a -->\n|win_CFA = 11|draw_CFA = 6|loss_CFA =13|gf_CFA = 23|ga_CFA = 34 <!-- CFR Arad -->\n|win_BMA = 12|draw_BMA = 3|loss_BMA =15|gf_BMA = 44|ga_BMA = 36 <!-- Minerul Baia Mare -->\n|win_GLO = 10|draw_GLO = 7|loss_GLO =13|gf_GLO = 29|ga_GLO = 38 <!-- Gloria Bistri\u021ba -->\n|win_GAZ = 10|draw_GAZ = 7|loss_GAZ =13|gf_GAZ = 28|ga_GAZ = 41 <!-- Gaz Metan Media\u0219 -->\n|win_ELE =  8|draw_ELE =10|loss_ELE =12|gf_ELE = 28|ga_ELE = 45 <!-- Electroputere Craiova -->\n|win_RE\u0218 = 10|draw_RE\u0218 = 5|loss_RE\u0218 =15|gf_RE\u0218 = 36|ga_RE\u0218 = 42 <!-- CSM Re\u0219i\u021ba -->\n|win_UMT =  7|draw_UMT =10|loss_UMT =13|gf_UMT = 26|ga_UMT = 33 <!-- UM Timi\u0219oara -->\n|win_VAG =  9|draw_VAG = 6|loss_VAG =15|gf_VAG = 28|ga_VAG = 39 <!-- Vagonul Arad -->\n\n<!--Team definitions (wikilinks in table)-->\n|name_CRI = [[FC Bihor Oradea|Cri\u0219ul Oradea]]\n|name_PTM = [[FC Politehnica Timi\u0219oara|Politehnica Timi\u0219oara]]\n|name_SIB = [[CSM Sibiu]]\n|name_COR = [[FC Corvinul Hunedoara|Corvinul Hunedoara]]\n|name_ANI = [[Minerul Anina]]\n|name_OLI = [[FC Olimpia Satu Mare|Olimpia Satu Mare]]\n|name_CUG = [[CF Metalurgistul Cugir|Metalurgistul Cugir]]\n|name_OLO = [[Olimpia Oradea]]\n|name_CFA = [[CFR Arad]]\n|name_BMA = [[CS Minaur Baia Mare (football)|Minerul Baia Mare]]\n|name_GLO = [[ACF Gloria Bistri\u021ba|Gloria Bistri\u021ba]]\n|name_GAZ = [[CS Gaz Metan Media\u0219|Gaz Metan Media\u0219]]\n|name_ELE = [[FC Caracal (2004)|Electroputere Craiova]]\n|name_RE\u0218 = [[CSM \u0218colar Re\u0219i\u021ba|CSM Re\u0219i\u021ba]]\n|name_UMT = [[CSP UM Timi\u0219oara|UM Timi\u0219oara]]\n|name_VAG = [[Vagonul Arad]]\n\n<!--Status-->\n|status_CRI=C,P\n|status_UMT=R\n|status_VAG=R\n\n<!--Table settings and rules-->\n|winpoints=2\n|show_limit=7\n|class_rules=1) Points 2) Goal difference; 3) Goals scored.\n\n<!--Qualification and relegation column definitions-->\n|res_col_header=PR\n|col_DA=green1 |text_DA= Promotion to [[1971\u201372 Divizia A|Divizia A]]\n|col_R=red1    |text_R = Relegation to [[Liga III|Divizia C]]\n}}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[1970\u201371 Divizia A]]\n\n==References==\n\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Liga II seasons}}\n<!--{{1970\u201371 in Romanian football}}-->\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1970-71 Divizia B}}\n[[Category:Liga II seasons]]\n[[Category:1970\u201371 in European association football leagues|Romania]]\n[[Category:1970\u201371 in Romanian football|2]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n | country                    = {{ROU}}\n | competition                = [[Liga II|Divizia B]]\n | season                     = 1970\u201371\n | teams                      = 32 (2x16)\n | promoted                   = [[ASA 1962 T\u00e2rgu Mure\u0219|ASA T\u00e2rgu Mure\u0219]]<br />[[FC Bihor Oradea|Cri\u0219ul Oradea]]\n | relegated                  = [[Metrom Bra\u0219ov]]<br />[[CSP UM Timi\u0219oara|UM Timi\u0219oara]]<br />[[CSM Flac\u0103ra Moreni|Flac\u0103ra Moreni]]<br />[[Vagonul Arad]]\n | league topscorer           = \n | biggest home win           =\n | biggest away win           =\n | highest scoring            =\n | matches                    = \n | total goals                =\n | longest wins               = \n | longest unbeaten           =\n | longest losses             =\n | highest attendance         = \n | lowest attendance          =\n | average attendance         =\n | prevseason                 = [[1969\u201370 Divizia B|1969\u201370]]\n | nextseason                 = [[1971\u201372 Divizia B|1971\u201372]]\n}}\n\nThe '''1970\u201371 [[Divizia B]]''' was the 31st season of the second tier of the [[Romanian football league system]].\n\nThe format has been maintained to two series, each of them having 16 teams. At the end of the season the winners of the series promoted to [[Liga I|Divizia A]] and the last two places from each series relegated to [[Liga III|Divizia C]].<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesr/roem2hist.html#71 rsssf.com]</ref><ref>[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_b/tables/1970_71.shtml romaniansoccer.ro]</ref>\n\n== Team changes ==\n{{col-begin|width=auto}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===To Divizia B===\n'''Promoted from [[1969\u201370 Divizia C|Divizia C]]'''\n* [[CSM Olteni\u021ba|SN Olteni\u021ba]]\n* [[CSP UM Timi\u0219oara|UM Timi\u0219oara]]\n* [[CSM Pa\u0219cani|CFR Pa\u0219cani]]\n* [[ACF Gloria Bistri\u021ba|Gloria Bistri\u021ba]]\n\n'''Relegated from [[1969\u201370 Divizia A|Divizia A]]'''\n* [[FC Bihor Oradea|Cri\u0219ul Oradea]]\n* [[ASA 1962 T\u00e2rgu Mure\u0219|ASA T\u00e2rgu Mure\u0219]]\n{{col-break|gap=5em}}\n\n===From Divizia B===\n'''Relegated to [[1970\u201371 Divizia C|Divizia C]]'''\n* [[CSM Suceava|Chimia Suceava]]\n* [[Chimia R\u00e2mnicu V\u00e2lcea]]\n* [[Gloria B\u00e2rlad]]\n* [[FC Drobeta-Turnu Severin|Metalul Turnu Severin]]\n\n'''Promoted to [[1970\u201371 Divizia A|Divizia A]]'''\n* [[AS Progresul Bucure\u0219ti|Progresul Bucure\u0219ti]]\n* [[FC CFR Timi\u0219oara|CFR Timi\u0219oara]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n=== Renamed teams ===\n''Metalul Hunedoara'' was renamed as [[FC Corvinul Hunedoara|Corvinul Hunedoara]].\n\n=== Other teams ===\n[[ASC O\u021belul Gala\u021bi|O\u021belul Gala\u021bi]] gave away its place in the Divizia B to [[FCM Dun\u0103rea Gala\u021bi|FC Gala\u021bi]], a newly formed team.<ref name=\"CFR\">[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/stiri/16668/evolutia-denumirilor-echipelor-de-a-lungul-anilor.htm Evolutia denumirilor echipelor de-a lungul anilor]. romaniansoccer.ro {{in lang|ro}}</ref>\n\n==League tables==\n=== Serie I ===\n{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WDL\n|source=[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_b/tables/1970_71.shtml romaniansoccer.ro]\n\n<!--Team positions-->\n|team1=ASA |team2=SPO |team3=TGV |team4=BR\u0102 |team5=GAL |team6=DGR\n|team7=MET |team8=CEA |team9=POR |team10=PA\u0218 |team11=SNO |team12=\u0218TI\n|team13=CMP |team14=PGL |team15=MBV |team16=FLA\n\n<!-- Team qualifications here (defined below)-->\n|result1=DA\n|result15=R\n|result16=R\n\n<!--Team results here-->\n|update=30 June 1971\n|win_ASA = 18|d